<p>Attached are written comments from AARP for the Advisory Council on Alzheimer's Research, Care and Services for their April 29 meeting tomorrow. We understand these comments will be shared with the Advisory Council. Please let us know if you have any questions or if there is anything else we need to do for submission of these comments.</p>
