<p>Alzheimer's Disease International is the worldwide federation of 78 national Alzheimer associations. Attached you may find a letter with our comments to the draft NAPA Act for your consideration.</p>
<p>I have also attached an overview of previous publications by the World Health Organization (WHO) that have any relationship with Alzheimer's disease and related disorders. The WHO will come out with a comprehensive report on 11 April.</p>
</td>
</tr></tbody></table><p><em><strong>ATTACHMENT #1:</strong></em></p>
