<p>Thank you for the opportunity to comment on the Draft National Plan to Address Alzheimer's Disease. The comments of the Alzheimer's Association are attached.</p>
<p>If you wish to discuss this or any other Alzheimer's issue, please feel free to reach out to Rachel Conant, Alzheimer's Association Director of Federal Affairs.</p>
