<li>Alzheimer's Association. Changing the Trajectory of Alzheimer's: A National Imperative. May 2010. <a href="http://www.alz.org/trajectory">http://www.alz.org/trajectory</a></li>
<li>For a profile of the particular challenges faced by those with Alzheimer's and other dementias who live alone, see the special report in the Alzheimer's Association's <em>2012 Alzheimer's Disease Facts and Figures</em>. <a href="http://www.alz.org/facts">http://www.alz.org/facts</a>.</li>
